:::

::::{.column-page .columns}

:::{.column width="25%"}


- accession matching
- fuzzy matching
- data cleaning utilities

:::

:::{.column width="75%"}

:::{.panel-tabset}

## fuzzy matching

```python
import wadoh_raccoon as tp

# input your dataframes and matching columns:
tp.fuzzZ(
    source=df1,
    reference=df2,
    first_name_src="first",
    last_name_src="last",
    dob_src="dob",
    first_name_ref="first",
    last_name_ref="last",
    dob_ref="dob"
)
```

